3-In-1 Pack

The Wow Super 3 Bath Set Bath Toy comes with 3 fun toys in one pack in a mix of vibrant and fun colors to keep your child delighted during their bath time.

Danny’s Diving Adventure

One of the toys is named after Danny who goes on a diving adventure whenever your child plays with this amazing toy. This toy comes with a diving board and a secret cabin.

Super Sub Sophie

Your child will love playing with Super Sub Sophie who will use the propeller in the water and hidden wheels on the land to have a great fun time.

Fireboat Felix

The other toy is named as Fireboat Felix
